data.name: 3 PLY MASKS
data.description:
## COMPOSITION
- 100% Non Woven (Polyphenylenether – PPE) fabric made of Viscose and Polyester Fibers

## STERILIZATION
- Non Sterile

## PRESENTATIONS
- White and Blue
- With Ties and Ear Loops
- Up to BFE ≥99%

## PERFORMANCE
- Water-repellent outer layer to prevent inhalation of large liquid droplets
- Adjustable Nose Fitting Clip
- With a non-irritating inner layer

## PROTECTION
- DENTAL
